{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ab09877fe2","title":"中央军委、军委文革小组关于冲击炮兵领导机关的文件","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4ca52671a5","index":0,"year":1967,"month":6,"day":26,"articleId":"ab09877fe2","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"军队和军事","id":"6f7a683373","type":"主题"},{"name":"中央军委、全军文革小组联合文件","id":"c41cae6e39","type":"发行机构"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"造反运动和派别斗争","id":"d48f0ea3e8","type":"主题"},{"name":"中央文件","id":"ef6e778547","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"中央文革","id":"ef71f03227","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"08551e78d3","type":"title","text":"中央军委、军委文革小组关于冲击炮兵领导机关的文件","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ab09877fe2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a28c28da11","type":"paragraph","text":"炮兵学院《红大》：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ab09877fe2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6583d2cac8","type":"paragraph","text":"你们在五月二十日冲击了炮兵领导机关，是严重地违背我们伟大领袖毛主席亲自签发的中央军委八项命令和北京市革命委员会的重要通告的行为，是完全错误的。你们不请示批准，擅自抓走炮兵副政委谢良同志，抢走炮兵领导机关的重要文件、材料，事后又不听从上级指示，至今没有送回，这是错上加错。六月六日，中共中央、国务院、中央军委、中央文革小组发布了七项通令。希望你们认真学习，对照检查，不要继续坚持错误。现在命令你们：","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ab09877fe2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"67fd5750e4","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）立即把谢良同志送回，并保证他的人身安全；","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ab09877fe2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e8a8f57a03","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）立即把你们抢走的所有文件、材料送回炮兵领导机关。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ab09877fe2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"023e4be1a8","type":"paragraph","text":"中央军委、军委文革","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ab09877fe2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"873f49b062","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六七年六月二十六日","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ab09877fe2","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}